                <p class="about-tagline">MAYSTERNYA 55 â€“<br>INDEPENDENT UKRAINIAN<br>THEATRE WITH<br>INTERNATIONAL ACTIVITIES<br>AND ITS OWN UNIQUE METHOD.</p>
